attributionInfo.brokerName: Main Street Realty of Pueblo, Inc

data.description: Looking for your high desert dreams? Look no further! Long vistas, mature trees, and fresh air welcome you to your new home in Pueblo West. Your 5 bedroom, 3 bath dream has all the room you need inside and out! A little over an acre on the outside, a 3-car garage, plus a super roomy 3,600 sq. ft on the inside. You'll find vaulted ceilings, an open concept living area with a gas-fireplace, and a kitchen with soft-close cabinets and stainless steel appliances, including a newer, high-end fridge, and double-oven to make entertaining easy. The walk-in pantry, breakfast nook, and laundry room (which features a deep, utility sink) really seal the deal on modern living luxuries. The spacious primary suite features a 5-piece bath and walk-in closet. The basement has rare 9 ft ceilings, 2 more bedrooms (to make 5 total), a wet bar, full bath, and game room! A great place for the teens or family fun! The large privacy fence in the back yard and covered patios in the back and front of the house offer endless ways to enjoy Colorado's beautiful weather and mountain views. Radon mitigation system and easy access to Hwy 50 and I-25.
